body:
You need to download the VOT2016 dataset first.

You can refer to this script.
https://github.com/foolwood/SiamMask/blob/master/data/get_test_data.sh

Make sure you have downloaded VOT dataset correctly. I had the same issue. It was because get_test_data.sh scripts were failing at some point but did not stop the process. The reason of failure was 'jq command not found'. Installing jq using `sudo apt-get install jq` solved my problem.
